            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"李飛飛的人工智能初創公司World Labs融資10億美元\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"647\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/iIOcsScB7P4QovgOHC9HpQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0Nw--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/b45478f0-0d47-11f1-ace6-fddcc7f0b172\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">李飛飛的人工智能初創公司World Labs融資10億美元</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
